pageContext.claim: “‘A lot of small & medium size enterprises are registering very good profit, sometimes record profits-there stocks are doing very well, low income workers are getting big raises. There are an awful lot of good things going on that weren’t during Pres. Obama’s Watch.’ Peter Morici”
pageContext.analysis: Trump regularly disparages Obama's handling of the economy, but the majority of economic trends that have continued under Trump's first term started under Obama and growth has stayed relatively stable.
